864
00:49:05,669 --> 00:49:08,589
I told you I'm not going to take over my dad's business!

865
00:49:08,589 --> 00:49:11,980
- Are you seriously... 
 - What did you just say?

866
00:49:16,540 --> 00:49:18,849
Photographer Shin's family is...

867
00:49:18,850 --> 00:49:21,080
Editor Na, I can explain.

868
00:49:28,670 --> 00:49:30,639
What the?

869
00:49:30,639 --> 00:49:33,070
What's up with her all of a sudden?

870
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:47,419
  Since I've lived longer than you, I'll say one thing.

871
00:49:47,419 --> 00:49:50,611
 Say the word "poor" backward.

872
00:49:50,611 --> 00:49:55,320
-  Family in turmoil. 
 - Right. You can become poor in an instant.

873
00:49:56,760 --> 00:50:00,179
  Do you want to become convenience store mates?

874
00:50:00,180 --> 00:50:03,650
 Per your advice, I'm saving up, too.

875
00:50:03,650 --> 00:50:07,939
