892
00:51:08,229 --> 00:51:11,299
I thought we were partners,

893
00:51:11,300 --> 00:51:14,990
but did you think of me as entertainment?

894
00:51:14,990 --> 00:51:16,889
- No, that's not it... 
 - If that's not it,

895
00:51:16,889 --> 00:51:19,819
why did you go along with my "save money" crap?

896
00:51:19,819 --> 00:51:21,359
"Let's target 1+1 items."

897
00:51:21,360 --> 00:51:22,940
"Let's be convenience store mates."

898
00:51:22,940 --> 00:51:25,379
