899
00:51:25,380 --> 00:51:27,260
 Probably because he took pity on you.

900
00:51:27,260 --> 00:51:30,379
How could he tell someone who was struggling to save up at your age

901
00:51:30,380 --> 00:51:32,070
that he doesn't have to worry about that kind of stuff?

902
00:51:32,070 --> 00:51:33,859
That he's from a rich family?

903
00:51:33,859 --> 00:51:37,229
He probably didn't want you to feel deprived by being honest.

904
00:51:37,230 --> 00:51:38,799
He's nice like that.

905
00:51:38,800 --> 00:51:41,310
Hyung!

906
00:51:41,310 --> 00:51:42,600
I'm sorry.

907
00:51:42,600 --> 00:51:43,909
What I did was wrong.

908
00:51:43,910 --> 00:51:46,779
Why apologize? You didn't do anything.

909
00:51:46,779 --> 00:51:49,229
The person who misunderstood is at fault.

910
00:51:49,229 --> 00:51:51,759
