913
00:51:57,280 --> 00:51:59,520
That's enough.

914
00:51:59,520 --> 00:52:01,110
Go. Go inside.

915
00:52:01,110 --> 00:52:04,539
I told you not to be nice to her.

916
00:52:04,539 --> 00:52:08,139
Even if you are nice to her, she'll misunderstand your intent completely.

917
00:52:08,139 --> 00:52:10,600
Then she'll stab you in the back without remorse.

918
00:52:10,600 --> 00:52:11,689
She's a scary woman!

919
00:52:11,690 --> 00:52:14,060
I said that's enough!

920
00:52:17,190 --> 00:52:18,930
Are you alright?

921
