928
00:52:53,900 --> 00:52:57,529
 Taking a cab to Seoul at this hour when they charge extra?

929
00:52:57,529 --> 00:52:59,190
Back off.

930
00:52:59,190 --> 00:53:01,719
You want to show up at a time like this?

931
00:53:01,719 --> 00:53:05,080
