932
00:53:06,310 --> 00:53:08,449
 Do you want to be poor?

933
00:53:08,450 --> 00:53:11,139
I know. I know!

934
00:53:11,140 --> 00:53:13,990
Beg or starve, it'll be my life!

935
00:53:13,990 --> 00:53:15,829
So go away!

936
00:53:15,829 --> 00:53:18,920
Don't ever show up in front of me again!

937
00:53:19,830 --> 00:53:21,500

938
