Sir! Can you drop me off over there?

939
00:53:24,409 --> 00:53:26,320
Okay.

940
00:53:34,130 --> 00:53:36,450
Na Zero Won is insane.

941
00:53:36,450 --> 00:53:38,720
If not, how could she...

942
00:53:38,720 --> 00:53:41,360
Ouch, that stings.

943
00:53:41,360 --> 00:53:43,600
Seriously! Who is she that I keep...

944
00:53:43,600 --> 00:53:46,289
How could I not waste my emotions?!

945
00:53:46,290 --> 00:53:47,809
How dare she push her CEO?

946
00:53:47,809 --> 00:53:50,200
On chestnuts?!

947
00:53:55,750 --> 00:53:57,930
Where's Editor Na Zero Won?

948
00:53:59,550 --> 00:54:01,830
She left.

949
00:54:01,830 --> 00:54:04,330
I can't believe how shameless she is.

950
00:54:04,330 --> 00:54:05,599
When she's the one at fault.

951
00:54:05,599 --> 00:54:10,139
She was so worried about you that she couldn't sleep a wink.

952
00:54:10,139 --> 00:54:11,709
Did she tell you that?

953
00:54:11,709 --> 00:54:13,409
You're really clueless.

954
00:54:13,409 --> 00:54:14,429
You know nothing.

955
00:54:14,429 --> 00:54:17,199
The reason she didn't go home earlier was because of you.

956
00:54:17,200 --> 00:54:19,569
She wanted to make it up to you, so she stayed behind.

957
00:54:19,569 --> 00:54:21,539
Why are you saying something so ridiculous now?

958
00:54:21,540 --> 00:54:23,799
She asked what kind of food you liked.

959
00:54:23,800 --> 00:54:26,749
She cooked kimchi stew because of you.

960
00:54:26,749 --> 00:54:28,249
What?

961
00:54:28,250 --> 00:54:29,130
Seriously.

962
00:54:29,131 --> 00:54:31,689
She made me promise not to tell you since it would seem like she was showing off,

963
00:54:31,690 --> 00:54:33,559
but I think you should know.

964
00:54:33,560 --> 00:54:38,180
You should know how truly sorry she is. You need to know.

965
00:54:49,950 --> 00:54:50,640
Hello?

966
00:54:50,641 --> 00:54:52,039
Hello, sir.

967
00:54:52,040 --> 00:54:53,389
It's me.

968
00:54:53,390 --> 00:54:55,709
I was wondering if you knew.

969
00:54:55,709 --> 00:54:57,030
