970
00:54:57,030 --> 00:55:00,340
Oh, the woman living in #707...

971
00:55:00,340 --> 00:55:03,239
 I heard she killed herself because of CEO Yoo.

972
00:55:03,239 --> 00:55:05,649
 What did he do that she killed herself?

973
00:55:05,650 --> 00:55:08,629
 He's a nasty man who only thinks about money.

974
00:55:08,629 --> 00:55:10,709
 She did a lot to resolve the misunderstanding

975
00:55:10,710 --> 00:55:12,719
 about you and the former tenant.

976
00:55:12,720 --> 00:55:16,280
 Hello. I'm the tenant living in #707.

977
00:55:16,280 --> 00:55:20,859
 I am writing this to clear up the rumor regarding #707.

978
00:55:20,859 --> 00:55:26,170
  The rumor that a former tenant killed herself here is indisputably false.

979
00:55:26,170 --> 00:55:30,050
  She put that up all night on every door.

980
00:55:30,050 --> 00:55:34,069
  She felt bad and didn't sleep a wink.

981
00:55:34,069 --> 00:55:35,199
 How can you sleep?

982
00:55:35,199 --> 00:55:36,809
 Are you sure you're repentant?

983
00:55:36,810 --> 00:55:39,209
 She stayed behind because of you.

984
00:55:39,209 --> 00:55:41,189
 She wanted to make it up to you.

985
00:55:41,189 --> 00:55:42,869
 I told you to go, but you insisted on staying.

986
00:55:42,869 --> 00:55:45,840
