1001
00:56:55,480 --> 00:57:02,910

1002
00:57:02,910 --> 00:57:04,960
 If I could fix my life

1003
00:57:04,960 --> 00:57:10,250
 like fixing broken parts...

1004
00:57:10,870 --> 00:57:18,880
 If I could do it over like painting over walls...

