I'm on my way to Seoul on business.

1012
00:57:52,009 --> 00:57:53,840
It's a coincidence we met.

1013
00:57:53,840 --> 00:57:58,460
Yes. You can be on your way now.

1014
00:57:58,460 --> 00:58:02,380
I think buses stopped running. Just get in.

1015
00:58:02,380 --> 00:58:05,339
It's okay. I'll go on my own.

1016
00:58:05,340 --> 00:58:06,229
If you get in now,

1017
00:58:06,229 --> 00:58:09,560
I'll forget you pushed me into a chestnut burr.

1018
00:58:09,560 --> 00:58:13,520
If not, I'll press charges.

1019
00:58:34,050 --> 00:58:37,570
I went too far earlier.

1020
00:58:37,570 --> 00:58:38,709
I'm sorry.

1021
00:58:38,710 --> 00:58:40,370
What?

1022
00:58:42,450 --> 00:58:44,750
Oh, well, I'm sorry, too.

1023
00:58:44,750 --> 00:58:47,230
How is your bottom?

1024
00:58:48,070 --> 00:58:52,910
Since we were both in the wrong, let's call it even and wipe the slate clean.

1025
00:58:52,910 --> 00:58:55,069
You don't have to move out either.

1026
00:58:55,069 --> 00:58:56,279
What?

1027
00:58:56,279 --> 00:59:00,789
You don't have to move out of #707.

1028
00:59:00,789 --> 00:59:02,329
Thank you.

1029
00:59:02,329 --> 00:59:04,569
No need to thank me.

1030
00:59:04,569 --> 00:59:08,989
I'm getting rent from a spare apartment.

1031
00:59:10,240 --> 00:59:11,220
In any case,

1032
00:59:11,220 --> 00:59:14,679
