00:59:14,680 --> 00:59:17,780
What if I hadn't driven by?

1034
00:59:27,290 --> 00:59:29,440
Look here, Editor Na Zero...

1035
00:59:30,710 --> 00:59:34,819
 She was so worried about you that she couldn't sleep a wink.

1036
00:59:34,819 --> 00:59:39,760
  She put that up all night on every door.

1037
