♫  That’ll never happen, I bet, you know  ♫

1044
01:01:23,190 --> 01:01:27,120
♫  I’m not the only one who thinks this  ♫

1045
01:01:27,120 --> 01:01:30,590
♫  You know this too  ♫

1046
01:01:31,590 --> 01:01:36,570
♫  This isn’t a dream  ♫

1047
01:01:36,570 --> 01:01:41,900
♫  But I started thinking about you   ♫

1048
01:01:41,900 --> 01:01:45,040
♫  You’ve come into my head  ♫

1049
01:01:45,040 --> 01:01:49,180
♫  Even the way you look at me  ♫

1050
